###read
GET http://localhost:6677/common-api/users

###registration
POST http://localhost:6677/common-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"Lexusss",
    "lastName":"Hamilton",
    "email":"lexuslalala123@gmail.com",
    "password":"lexus123344",
    "role":"USER",
    "profileImageUrl":"hamilton.jpg"
}

###login
POST http://localhost:6677/common-api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"lexusla123@gmail.com",
    "password":"lexusla12345"
}

###logout
GET http://localhost:6677/common-api/users/logout



###Read articles of all authors
GET http://localhost:6677/user-api/articles

###Add comment to an article
