Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleId":"69b3dc0d7c380791c562c41a",
    "comment":"FORREALLLLL."
}

###update password
PUT http://localhost:6677/common-api/users/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword":"lexusla12345",
    "newPassword":"lexusla12345"
}